  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL19">
<l>kuṭaticai muṭiyai vaittuk kuṇaticai pātam nīṭṭi</l>
<l>vaṭaticai piṉpu kāṭṭit teṉticai yilaṅkai nōkkik</l>
<l>kaṭalniṟak kaṭavu ḷentai yaravaṇait tuyilu mākaṇ</l>
<l>ṭuṭaleṉak kuruku mālō veṉceykē ṉulakat tīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Seeing the way the ocean-hued God, my father sleeps on the serpent bed,</l>
<l rend="indent">placing [His] head in the western direction,</l>
<l rend="indent">stretching [His] feet towards the eastern direction,</l>
<l rend="indent">showing [His] back to the northern direction,</l>
<l rend="indent">and facing Laṅkā in the southern direction,</l>
<l>my body will melt, ālō! What shall I do, O you people of the world!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
